B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, Jaime VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\">13.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-1\">13.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_44\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a>, Jaime VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404232946\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.070 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2105/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9734/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10245/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1162/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 10659/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   50.122      1 -total\n 83.26%   41.734     30 Template:Ref\n 46.56%   23.337     30 Template:Ref/core\n 10.69%    5.358      1 Template:References\n  5.71%    2.864      2 Template:Quote\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:31385-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404232946 and revision id 290852\n -->\n",
